-- Juncker Says He Won’t Stay on as Head of Eurogroup, APA Reports
-- B y   Z o e   S c h n e e w e i s s
-- 2012-04-03T16:42:27Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-03/juncker-says-he-won-t-stay-on-as-head-of-eurogroup-apa-reports.html
Luxembourg Prime Minister Jean- Claude Juncker said he won’t continue to lead the group of euro-
area finance ministers after his term ends this summer, Austria
Press Agency reported, citing Juncker.  German Finance Minister  Wolfgang Schaeuble  would be a
“good candidate,” Juncker told APA, adding that there were
others as well.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Zoe Schneeweiss in Vienna at 
